rComments: Not gunna lie, I felt that the 2 FLS courses I took in 1st year were a waste of time and I only took them for the credits; however, this year I had the pleasure to be in this prof's class twice and I absolutely would recommend her. Every class I learn something new and valuable, so I feel like I am not wasting my time. Also she is super nice!!
Amazing prof, very helpful and understanding. Makes class fun and easy to understand. Assignments and exams are fair, if you show up to class and pay attention you'll do great.
She tries to make the class fun but she doesn't actually teach relevant material. We hardly did any exercises that would actually help prepare us for the exam.
